                             double scenarioProb,
                             double[][][] loadScenarioData,

        Construct a full load scenario (all hours of all days in the scenario).
        Parameters:
        caseName -
        scenarioNumber -
        scenarioProb -
        loadScenarioData - day x hour x zone loads. Assumes data is arranged from day 1 to DAY_MAX.
        copyProfiles - if true, will copy each array. See: DailyLoadProfile.setLoadByHour(int, double[], boolean). This constructor does not validate the data. Call validate(String, int, int), if need to make sure LoadScenario is correct.
